sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'; import Card from '@material-ui/core/Card' import CardContent from '@material-ui/core/CardContent'; import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button' import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography'; const StudentHome = props=>{ let toDoArr; let closedArr; if(props.toGrade.length>0){ toDoArr=props.toGrade.map((e,i)=>( {e.name} Team: {e.team} Overall Grade: {e.overallGrade}/5 )) } if(props.toGrade.length===0){ toDoArr=props.toGrade.map(e=>( No students created yet! )) } if(props.closedArr.length>0){ closedArr=props.closedArr.map((e,i)=>( {e.name} Members: {e.members.map(name=>{name} | )} Overall Grade: {e.overAll}/5 )) } if(props.closedArr.length===0){ closedArr=props.closedArr.map(e=>( No teams created yet )) } return( All Teams {closedArr} Students {toDoArr} ) } export default StudentHome
